Ken Programming Language
========================

Ken transpile to portable C11 code. The transpiler is written in C and is currently in early development. Do not use this in production.

Our goal of creating this Programming is to code safety but the syntax is probably similar with C or HolyC

Code sample
-----------

This is our main goal of how the Ken programming language syntax is

I8 main()
{
    println("Hello world");
    return 0;
}

str greet(str name)
{
    print(name);
    println(" is a good person");
}

Status
======

Work in progress. Things will break.
